{"tid":2299882,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請問now今日係咪又炒車","createTime":"2020-11-25T05:37:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T08:34:52.000Z","uid":58841,"like":20,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"729106d2ecd2ba9ac2ee1a9d8ad1a115b3b8e617","tid":2299882,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T05:37:00.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=414152\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414152&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=63575493\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fmobile%2FeditorsChoice%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D414152&h=69f7daf0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/mobile/editorsChoice/player?newsId=414152</a><br />\n<br />\n入面有一段<br />\n<br />\n同一日有美國行政官員表示，<span class=\"red\">特朗普簽署相關文件，批准向拜登每日提供最新機密情報</span>，但行政官員仍在處理相關程序，暫時未知道拜登甚麼時候和在甚麼地方聽取匯報。<br />\n<br />\n之後我睇到呢段野原來係quote左媒CBS<br />\n<br />\nPresident Trump has agreed to allow President-elect Biden to begin receiving the President's Daily Brief, a classified intelligence report by the Office of the Director of National Intelligence, two U.S. officials and <span class=\"red\">a source familiar confirmed to CBS News</span>. Mr. Trump's decision comes after the federal agency that oversees the presidential transition formally started the process Monday evening.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cbsnews.com/news/trump-presidential-intelligence-briefing-biden/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Ftrump-presidential-intelligence-briefing-biden%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=deb8602e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.cbsnews.com/news/trump-presidential-intelligence-briefing-biden/</a><br />\n<br />\n但係過左7個鐘仲未有其他右媒同白宮證實呢樣野係堅<br />\n<br />\n我反而就係侵個gab睇到呢個post<br />\n<br />\nShould President Trump concede to Biden? Poll Results: No: 190,593 (98.9%) Yes: 2,181 (1.1%) Total Votes: 192,774. @gregkellyusa @newsmax For the good of our Country we must prevail!<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://gab.com/realdonaldtrump/posts/105268281240812584\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgab.com%2Frealdonaldtrump%2Fposts%2F105268281240812584&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKMls9Dgy9T8na9BfJ9hiblc%3D&h=649f345d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://gab.com/realdonaldtrump/posts/105268281240812584</a><br />\n<br />\n有冇全能既連登仔可以解釋下志氣高昂唔認輸既特朗普有咩動機會俾拜登睇國安機密<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果我炒車請提供官方source<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/stop.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3af6986f5c860b7e0c0fd71f42be88df627abcea","tid":2299882,"uid":308915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:10:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f89f9d50f38079540576f6e0fcca8387106cc37b","tid":2299882,"uid":72362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"仲睇now news? 上次trump認輸單野 唔夠洗一鑊?"},{"pid":"cfd0f3fa8624825ada78887cdb9012023650abf4","tid":2299882,"uid":50275,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f89f9d50f38079540576f6e0fcca8387106cc37b","tid":2299882,"uid":72362,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:13:25.000Z","msg":"仲睇now news? 上次trump認輸單野 唔夠洗一鑊?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T07:24:49.000Z","msg":"Now<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea